{"tid":2403320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃埔業主趕移民    減60萬沽","createTime":"2021-02-11T04:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T04:34:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fdae113008da240b0e032b6a028af322af14a269","tid":2403320,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200620/s00011/254895cbec67d9ff8e77d0508b59b3c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200620%2Fs00011%2F254895cbec67d9ff8e77d0508b59b3c9.jpg&h=5541927f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再有業主移民減價賣樓。中原袁顯岸表示，紅磡黃埔花園2期15座中高層G室兩房單位，實用面積466方呎，原業主因舉家移民決定沽貨，上月初開價840萬元，累減60萬元，以780萬元易手，呎價16,738元。新買家為同區上車客，見銀行估價可達800萬元，議價後即拍板入市。"}]}